name: Bikini Bottom Migration Test
description:
Want to move to Bikini Bottom? Pass this test first, see if you can get used to the challenging life there. Even though you like jellyfish, I don't think you wanna touch it when it flashes. And you always know who is the biggest trouble maker at Bikini Beach. The best way to avoid trouble is not touching him at all! Wish you good luck! 

Use AWSD to move, Space to jump.
